1.0.1.name: wordpress/hpbtool
1.0.1.description:
"hpb Dashboard" plug-in has the function which imports data created by "Home Page Builder 17" into WordPress website. "Home Page Builder 17" is a software which assists people to design their websites. Moreover, this plug-in has the following functions elsewhere.

  • customizes the dashboard
  • arranges social buttons
  • sets up inquiry form
  • sets up access analysis
